{"tid":2108042,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【西門梓敬認可】初選後配票心法　分區配票最合成本效益達成 35+","createTime":"2020-07-14T09:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T04:29:52.000Z","uid":85252,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"280548b2c60d77e3f9e79dfdada9f447a3223469","tid":2108042,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"個半月前有絲打提出分區配票概念 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初選後係時候拎返出來傾﹗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/96810286_193035118363372_7323297802392436736_n_KWaKo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F96810286_193035118363372_7323297802392436736_n_KWaKo_1200x0.png&h=c0575242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分區配票優勢<br />\n1. 配票數據基礎準確龐大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靠住 2019 年區議會黃藍總計 <span class=\"red\">293萬</span>票做配票基礎同推演<br />\n比起用初選 60 萬只有黃營票來得踏實<br />\n<br />\n2. 高效益選舉工程 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分區配票可以方便候選人同助選團隊集中火力針對自己的細區做選舉工程<br />\nBanner／街站／宣傳品／地區性 SMS 嘅成本可以大幅壓低<br />\n更重要係節省候選人穿梭多區宣傳的<span class=\"red\">時間成本</span><br />\n譬如，新東候選人由上水走到將軍澳，飛的都半粒鐘啦<br />\n<br />\n3. 操作極為簡單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n統計學方式（如生日日期／身份證號碼）配票的概念理論上雖然可行<br />\n但看似簡單的方法卻對數學較差的群體平添壓力<br />\n<br />\n4. 避免內鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初選兩日都遇上尹佬票站唔遮自己名嘅質疑<br />\n用其他全地圖嘅配票方法，難免會令地區樁腳陷入<span class=\"red\">情義兩難全</span>的窘境<br />\n分區配票就可以定好助選義工去相應嘅區，投返自己人<br />\n<br />\n5. 棄選非最有效 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民主陣營應該集中火力谷初選出線者<br />\n花費一分一毫希望偷雞搶位嘅人，自己撫心自問對唔對得住手足<br />\n<br />\n附上，網頁解說同示範<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tacticalvoting.github.io/leg2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftacticalvoting.github.io%2Fleg2020&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=2c9d776d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tacticalvoting.github.io/leg2020</a><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n原 post<br />\n<br />\n【突發】嚇壞支那辦的立會必勝法 琼子見到也哭了<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2013515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2013515</a>"},{"pid":"9d6b2f3141f0181e9e24b296c0353ec7ddbdb06d","tid":2108042,"uid":85252,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"補返西門梓敬條 link 先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_2WLsufmULU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_2WLsufmULU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D385&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ce1edecc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_2WLsufmULU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=385</a>"},{"pid":"c90679e5351308c111dfb67ba960a394ff833789","tid":2108042,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"其實用票站去配票係最好"},{"pid":"a68a79e5a1256dceee1df01587bac5824830c7e0","tid":2108042,"uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得好醒得你諗到咁⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之大前提係全部人都要守規矩<br />\n講咗邊個喺邊區就邊區<br />\n<br />\n總有人怕落選偷雞去其他區搶票"},{"pid":"570957aa9ae96678724b2434ca3dd08698ec3235","tid":2108042,"uid":195690,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"好過擲骰仔"},{"pid":"4dbfb4661081305b7845d50fff5e4986b91aa997","tid":2108042,"uid":195690,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"上次區議會選舉，有幾多人含涙投白鴿，為左踢走建制，其實只要目標一致，配票都會成功"},{"pid":"b5a430c013f7f6fc60eec78ab8d1c6af66e55794","tid":2108042,"uid":85252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4dbfb4661081305b7845d50fff5e4986b91aa997","tid":2108042,"uid":195690,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score"