n啲人會傾向投佢endorse 嘅人<br />\n<br />\n民主陣營要諗埋呢個因素<br />\n去令成件事易啲推+無咁多拗撬"},{"pid":"38e319b6f0c242f73f6bb7f620c30c565c948d26","tid":2108042,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90cab59ec6365a649e254b9fc33c43568e712b36","tid":2108042,"uid":178651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"仆街仔西門梓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:09:47.000Z","msg":"恐同深櫃基佬 西門梓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c13f8e7144e9cba3039db7987e552fa88bc66a","tid":2108042,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da5cbfcec99f7811dff4135779dea226f30012f","tid":2108042,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a68a79e5a1256dceee1df01587bac5824830c7e0","tid":2108042,"uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得好醒得你諗到咁⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之大前提係全部人都要守規矩<br />\n講咗邊個喺邊區就邊區<br />\n<br />\n總有人怕落選偷雞去其他區搶票"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"有啲地區工作做得好嘅<br />\n啲人會傾向投佢endorse 嘅人<br />\n<br />\n民主陣營要諗埋呢個因素<br />\n去令成件事易啲推+無咁多拗撬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"啲區點分的確係要靠參選人自己傾掂數"},{"pid":"e1acf726b78b13372421b2016c6b246302129fd3","tid":2108042,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38e319b6f0c242f73f6bb7f620c30c565c948d26","tid":2108042,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90cab59ec6365a649e254b9fc33c43568e712b36","tid":2108042,"uid":178651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"仆街仔西門梓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:09:47.000Z","msg":"恐同深櫃基佬 西門梓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"畢咗嗌幾十年仲要強調自己名校畢業<br />\n反證自己幾十年來無嘢可以 claim credit<br />\n核撚突<br />\n<br />\n麥明詩都唔會提自己 10A 好巴閉啦"},{"pid":"ae3f8b51e8bddd7aa54f41b9e5083cc5687a37c3","tid":2108042,"uid":129393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"其實組隊投票得唔得<br />\n如果你個地區分區，泛民aim 6席，你就搵齊6個人組隊，一人投一個<br />\n<br />\n用票站或者分區來配票，會唔會怕有啲死硬派唔肯？"},{"pid":"f1c0ea75515f7615380545f26f47bd220f72ed0f","tid":2108042,"uid":112094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ae3f8b51e8bddd7aa54f41b9e5083cc5687a37c3","tid":2108042,"uid":129393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"其實組隊投票得唔得<br />\n如果你個地區分區，泛民aim 6席，你就搵齊6個人組隊，一人投一個<br />\n<br />\n用票站或者分區來配票，會唔會怕有啲死硬派唔肯？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"佢個網有解釋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tacticalvoting.github.io/leg2020/#faq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftacticalvoting.github.io%2Fleg2020%2F%23faq&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=d80ef790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tacticalvoting.github.io/leg2020/#faq</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>而「6人成行」的配票方法除了操作複雜，還會造成政黨地區樁腳與策略選民的巨大衝突，一方面樁腳要為自身政黨拉票，確保勝選，另一方面該區的策略選民又要呼籲選民分散投票，結局難免是地區資源豐厚的政黨樁腳極力守住地區得票，而其他地區又同時為該政黨配了票，最後就是該政黨成了表面風光的票王票后，但民主陣營卻把地區資源匱乏的參選名單押在最後一席的豪賭上。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"79cbb232cda092f865e6405eee640801746cd301","tid":2108042,"uid":116793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7afe0fa1f8ae260a1ac09936e7ccf8d5fe4f145","tid":2108042,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6b2f3141f0181e9e24b296c0353ec7ddbdb06d","tid":2108042,"uid":85252,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"補返西門梓敬條 link 先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_2WLsufmULU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_2WLsufmULU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D385&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ce1edecc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_2WLsufmULU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=385</a>"},"cit